# Manifests in OpenMPI v4.1.2 and remains an issue on v5.0.3
# Bug: https://github.com/open-mpi/ompi/issues/12584
# ASan Build with LeakSantizer complains about leaks in openmpi lib.
leak:openmpi

# WatcherServer singleton allocates a small buffer in attach_devices() that
# intentionally outlives main(). Triggered by any test that opens mock devices.
leak:tt::tt_metal::WatcherServer::Impl::attach_devices
